# Build a Data Science Api: Write an API

## What is an API
It is a programming layer that serves as a gateway for your applicacation.

## Pros
* One supprt all kinds of apps, all kinds of platforms and all kinds of languages.
* Documentation is fairly straighforward to produce. Data, endpoint and output 
* The back-end code can be anything you want it to be
* Simplifies production efforts and time

# Cons
* More code to maintain
  * code versioning needs to be tracked closely
* Can present a security risk
* Perfomance monitoring/optimization can be difficult to track/fix



